{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9a7fb3420","title":"关于组织外地来京革命师生进行政治军事训练的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e13996d4aa","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"e9a7fb3420"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d56298f3fd","type":"paragraph","text":"接见在京部队时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"3f812386c3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十月十三日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"4cacb6e64a","type":"paragraph","text":"下次接见，柔取阅兵式的办法。不管多少人，解放军要统统包下来，经过训练，把解放军的光荣传统、三八作风、三大纪律、八项注意，带到全国各地去。三大纪律八项注意歌，人人要会唱，我也要会唱。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"83b301df45","type":"paragraph","text":"A","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"db6e1cde56","type":"paragraph","text":"传关于粗罐外地来京革命师生进行政治","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"358584bde8","type":"paragraph","text":"重事动辣的指示","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"b040952078","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"6727cfb107","type":"paragraph","text":"由军队负责将外地来京革命师生，按解放军的编制，编成班、排、连、营、团、师。编好后，进行训练，学习政治，学习解放军，学习林彪同志和周恩来总理的讲，学习三大纪律，八项注意，学习解放军的三八作风，学习编队队形，学习队列基本动作，学习步法，每个人都要学会三大纪律八项注意的歌子，使外地的革命师生有秩序地接受检阅。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"f192869d5c","type":"paragraph","text":"对陈伯达同志《两个月来运动的","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"c7e4a08d19","type":"paragraph","text":"总精》的指示","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"afc0703f95","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十月二十四日）","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"30f5cafbd4","type":"paragraph","text":"直送伯达同志，改稿看过，很好。抓革命、促生产这两句是否在什么地方加进去，请考虑。要大量印成小册子，每个支部、每个红卫兵小队超码有一份。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"fb98c48bce","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央政治局汇报会截上的融需","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"18384a5950","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十月二十四日）","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"a33045f35d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：“有什么可怕呢？你们看了李雪案的简报没有？他的两个孩子跑出去，回来后教育李雪率说：“我们这里的老首长，为什么那么害怕红卫兵呢？我们又没打你们”。天家就是不检讨。伍修权家有四个孩子，分为四派，有很多同学到他家里去，有时十几个人。接触多了就没有什么可怕了了，觉得他们很可爱。自己要教育人，教育者要先受教育。你们不通。不敢见红卫兵，不和学生说质，做官当老爷，先不敢见面，后不敢讲，革了几十年的命，越来越鑫了，刘××给江××的信，批评了江××说他鑫，他自己就聪明了吗？","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"},{"id":"47cf096e4b","type":"paragraph","text":"272","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420"}],"page":{"id":"3a1f5363c3","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e9a7fb3420","start":285,"end":285}}}},"__N_SSG":true}